This paper deals with image captioning, which is a task in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the role of model architectures and learning objectives, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates metrics for image relevance and language similarity, which are topics in information retrieval (cs.IR).
